'''Vokkaligara Sangha''' is a democratically elected Vokkaliga community organisation that was founded in 1906 in [[Bengaluru]] to promote the social, cultural and educational aspirations of the [[Vokkaliga]] community. Vokkaligara Sangha has its headquarters in [[Bengaluru]], Karnataka and has many affiliated regional sanghas. Today, Vokkaligara Sangha is one of the top community organisations in Karnataka State that serves the Vokkaliga community in different areas.<ref>http://vokkaligar.blogspot.in/2010/01/blog-post.html</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.daijiworld.com/news/newsDisplay.aspx?newsID=378881|title=Mumbai: Vokkaliga Sangha celebrates Vokkaliga Mahotsava 2016|access-date=2018-05-10}}</ref>

==Management==

Vokkaligara Sangha has a well structured election system. Elected members handle key roles in Sangha's activities and Sangha owned institutions. Elected members serve as community representatives of their regions.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-karnataka/vokkaligara-sangha-poll-results/article5564779.ece|title=Vokkaligara Sangha poll results|last=Reporter|first=Staff|date=2014-01-11|work=The Hindu|access-date=2018-05-10|last2=Reporter|first2=Staff|language=en-IN|issn=0971-751X}}</ref><ref>http://vokkaligarasangha.com/management.html</ref>

==Institutions==

Sangha owns reputed educational institutions like [[Bangalore Institute of Technology]]<ref>https://www.admissionbackup.com/management-quota/direct-admission/bangalore-institute-of-technology/</ref> and [[Kempegowda Institute of Medical Sciences]] (KIMS).

The Sangha runs the following prominent institutions, among others:<ref>http://vokkaligarasangha.com/facilities.html</ref>
* Vokkaligara Sangha Dental College and Hospital
* vv puram Arts and Commerce College{{Citation needed|date=November 2017}}
* vv puram science College{{Citation needed|date=November 2017}}
* KempeGowda Institute of Physiotherapy
* Kempegowda Nursing College
* SKFG College of Arts and Commerce{{Citation needed|date=November 2017}}
* Vokkaligara Sangha Nursery Primary and Middle School
* Vokkaligara Sangha ITI
* vv puram Evening College of Arts & Commerce College{{Citation needed|date=November 2017}}
* vv puram Law College{{Citation needed|date=November 2017}}
* KempeGowda Medical Hospital and Research Centre
* vv puram Institute of Pharmacy{{Citation needed|date=November 2017}}
* Sri GandhadaKavalu Junior College{{Citation needed|date=November 2017}}
* Vokkaligara Sangha High School
* Vokkaligara Sangha Free Students Hostel

